title: NEFF ALTERNATOR HOODY
description: Welcome to the Never Before Seen Neff Alternator Hoodie. This Hoody features 3 interchangeable pockets so you can zip of and zip off new looks everyday. With the 1st ever removable hoody pockets this hoody is one of a kind and you are sure to impress. Visit www.neffheadwear.com for more info.
